Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.15,0:00:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,She's founded a company?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.02,0:00:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,For Gundams?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.27,0:00:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It was Ms. Miorine's own idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.93,0:00:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,She solicited investment and
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.73,0:00:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,bought out some of Peil's and Shin Sei's\Ndevelopment teams on the spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.48,0:00:13.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I almost fainted.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.95,0:00:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Rich girls do everything flashier.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.55,0:00:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,She must have an ulterior motive.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.61,0:00:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Four.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.22,0:00:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Doubt.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.86,0:00:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.54,0:00:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Suletta's been having trouble\Never since she transferred here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.01,0:00:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You will have trouble\Nwith men in the near future.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.37,0:00:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! That's the last thing I need!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.21,0:00:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Shouldn't we just let her do as she likes?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.79,0:00:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's got nothing to do with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.78,0:00:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's got plenty to do with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.30,0:00:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Miorine?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.59,0:00:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What'd you bring the Princess here for?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.80,0:00:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm setting up the company here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.01,0:00:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.64,0:00:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,GUND-ARM, Inc. will be run\Nby me and everyone here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.06,0:00:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it. You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.57,0:00:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.22,0:00:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Say what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.49,0:00:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Now the company's launched,\Nthere's a ton of things to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.74,0:00:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Don't talk like we've agreed to this!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.94,0:00:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,And why us, any--
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.62,0:01:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be properly paid.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.69,0:01:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Any other questions? None, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.46,0:01:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.07,0:01:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I apologize for whatever\NMs. Miorine's doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.04,0:01:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What will your company\Nbe doing with Gundams, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.52,0:01:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.96,0:01:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,what I'm about to figure out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.98,0:02:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,That Spacian turd!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.48,0:02:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Chuchu, class is in session.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.44,0:02:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay with this, Nika?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.36,0:02:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do we need to obey her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.85,0:02:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.72,0:03:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if it means\NI get to work on Aerial...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.31,0:03:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And if the company is successful,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.19,0:03:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,it's a chance to prove that\NEarthians can do as well as Spacians.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.78,0:03:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm not gonna wait on\Nsome selfish Spacian bimbo!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.55,0:03:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's breaking!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.71,0:03:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Are you okay with this, Nuno?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.62,0:03:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.13,0:03:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It depends on the salary.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.13,0:03:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's mighty, I won't complain.\NIf it's meager, I'll slack off.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.26,0:03:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, no, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.72,0:03:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We're talking Gundams! And witches!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.84,0:03:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,They're all cursed!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.39,0:03:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to learn about business, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.55,0:03:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't this perfect?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.36,0:03:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a perfect disaster!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.30,0:03:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The group's big shots are--
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.75,0:03:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Martin Upmont!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.52,0:03:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.23,0:03:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,If you can't be quiet, leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.70,0:03:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm very sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.49,0:03:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Count me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.98,0:03:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And what do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.78,0:03:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Depends on what we'd be doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.73,0:03:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Aliya! Mr. Till!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.03,0:03:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have any clue where Ms. Miorine is?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.34,0:03:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to know more about Aerial?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.93,0:03:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Our company will be handling\NGundams, so I have a lot of questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.85,0:03:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Is Ariel really safe?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.46,0:04:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Can she be mass-produced?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.64,0:04:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And why develop her when you\Nhad to hide that she was a Gundam?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.23,0:04:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I just sent you all of Ariel's past data.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.43,0:04:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,People who want Gundams
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.93,0:04:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,will trust numbers\Nover your words or mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.27,0:04:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.00,0:04:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, mass production\Nis impossible at this point.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.37,0:04:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,We haven't pinned down\Nthe basic elements of the GUND Format,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.73,0:04:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,and aren't ready to accumulate data.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.46,0:04:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll have to begin with analysis.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.47,0:04:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Gundam's curse\Nis a heavier burden than you think.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.64,0:04:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's what he meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.76,0:04:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.08,0:04:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.68,0:04:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.39,0:04:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.99,0:04:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,say to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.05,0:04:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,that Aerial wasn't a Gundam?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.86,0:04:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Aerial is family to us, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.97,0:05:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,She's not really cursed, is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.33,0:05:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Does it frighten you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.92,0:05:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.91,0:05:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's your arm, Mom. Same as always.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.91,0:05:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you. But even so,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.82,0:05:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,people can't help being afraid\Nof the unknown.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.56,0:05:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,And they try to\Nkeep that fear at a distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.52,0:05:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Or even attack it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.40,0:05:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Gundams will remain in\Npeople's minds as forbidden machines.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.19,0:05:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Even so, I wanted to protect you two
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.78,0:05:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,from the curse's abominable flame.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.61,0:05:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.02,0:05:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.56,0:05:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It was all for us, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.74,0:05:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,But of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.98,0:05:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You're my beloved daughters.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.08,0:05:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for my silly question!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.52,0:05:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,From now on, I'll protect Aerial too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.65,0:05:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,For your sake, Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.16,0:05:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Be sure to tell everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.45,0:06:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It's safe to have Gundams by their side.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.79,0:06:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.43,0:06:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway... Wasn't there something\Nmore important to ask your mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.26,0:06:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.25,0:06:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Like why you're able to pilot Aerial\Nwithout suffering any harm.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.41,0:06:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you know she's a Gundam...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.56,0:06:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,aren't you scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.93,0:06:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all!\NAerial and I have always been family!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.28,0:06:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Have it your way...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.68,0:06:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Mercurian Miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.78,0:06:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you make up with your mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.86,0:06:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.81,0:06:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, I--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.86,0:06:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Suletta.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.56,0:06:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell that creep a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.16,0:06:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You're mad again?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.94,0:06:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't want me\Ngetting close to your groom?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.40,0:06:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You only want to know more about\NAerial for your company's sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.59,0:06:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,And what about your company?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.45,0:06:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You have absolutely no time to sit back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.90,0:06:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You managed to make it through there,\Nbut your investors aren't philanthropists.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.78,0:06:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Depending on your business plan,\Nyou might go back to zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.17,0:06:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you trying to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.76,0:06:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not let me take over the company?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.81,0:06:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.68,0:06:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,On what terms?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.73,0:07:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.18,0:07:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Marriage to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.35,0:07:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! M-M...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.46,0:07:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Oh, shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.90,0:07:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,M-M-Marriage?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.79,0:07:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\an8}This ship will now...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.79,0:07:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's discuss this again soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.43,0:07:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\an8}...enter a docking course.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.73,0:07:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye now, Mercurian Miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.46,0:07:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.46,0:07:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\an8}Please be seated and fasten your...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.28,0:07:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I think I get it. It's you, Ms. Miorine!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.06,0:07:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\an8}We will now enter...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.49,0:07:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\an8}...a docking course.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.70,0:07:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Shaddiq is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.25,0:07:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\an8}Please fasten your seatbelts.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.49,0:07:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,in l-l-l-love with...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.54,0:07:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't kid yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.99,0:07:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.56,0:07:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just that he...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.54,0:07:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,was raised in an orphanage\Nrun by the Grassley family.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.04,0:07:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.35,0:07:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That guy will do whatever it takes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.92,0:07:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let your guard down.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.94,0:07:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.73,0:07:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,As President Miorine instructed,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.68,0:07:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I've organized the disclosure\Ninformation for the investors.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.39,0:07:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You've accepted your fate already?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.10,0:07:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Putting aside minor registrations,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.97,0:07:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,there are a lot of things\Nwe have to decide.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.52,0:07:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Like salary, wages, bonuses, and raises.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.98,0:07:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,They're all money matters, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.86,0:07:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Those things are important too, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.69,0:07:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to start\Nwith articles of incorporation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.87,0:07:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Articles?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.15,0:08:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,They're documents that establish\Nthe nature of the company.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.91,0:08:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The company's name, its founders,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.07,0:08:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,the total number of authorized shares...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.33,0:08:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The specifics will be written\Nin the company's business plan, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.76,0:08:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to decide\Nthe company's mission, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.54,0:08:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever it is,\Nit should be something profitable.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.14,0:08:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,From what Suletta's mom said,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.84,0:08:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,unless the GUND Format's safety is proven,\Nwe won't be able to manufacture Gundams.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.94,0:08:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What about Peil's Gundam?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.55,0:08:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I think they called it...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.63,0:08:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Pharact.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.19,0:08:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Did it use technology\Ndifferent from Aerial's?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.27,0:08:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't say without looking into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.82,0:08:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,According to the documents\Nwe received from Peil,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.61,0:08:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,the cost of building one Pharact unit was...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.66,0:08:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,This much.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.99,0:08:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.07,0:08:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,How many units of my mobile suit\Ncould you buy with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.83,0:08:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,After buying out Shin Sei's and Peil's\Ndevelopment teams,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.37,0:08:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,what are the company's assets?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.79,0:08:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,This much.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.05,0:08:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.08,0:08:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not even enough\Nto feed Giko and the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.85,0:08:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Manufacturing is far beyond\Nour dreams at this point.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.01,0:09:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's just make a rosy business plan\Nto raise everyone's expectations.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.22,0:09:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Then people will come to finance us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.38,0:09:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What are we gonna sell, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.74,0:09:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.66,0:09:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Normally, selling them as weapons\Nwould seem the most reasonable plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.40,0:09:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that would be\Nthe natural thing to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.87,0:09:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.29,0:09:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What? It would make money, wouldn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.96,0:09:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a war orphan, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.23,0:09:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,There are tons of kids like me on Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.04,0:09:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,If we're only selling\Nto Earthians, I'm for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.03,0:09:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But that would mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.88,0:09:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Earth would become a battlefield again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.66,0:09:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.92,0:09:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.21,0:09:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,In the first place, selling only\Nto Earthians isn't even realistic.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.67,0:09:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,We're a part of the Benerit Group, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.23,0:09:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.76,0:09:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you siding with the Spacians?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.18,0:09:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not what I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.60,0:09:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't come here to build mobile suits.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.64,0:09:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I love money, for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.58,0:09:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Even so, I don't feel like\Nprofiting off killing machines.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.83,0:09:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,At the end of the day,\Nyou're just another spoiled kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.36,0:09:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.48,0:10:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,E-Everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.91,0:10:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't fight like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.57,0:10:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,She's right. Calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.29,0:10:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What about you, Nika?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.54,0:10:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.20,0:10:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,If Spacians do as they please\Nwith the mobile suits we build,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.18,0:10:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,could you handle it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.84,0:10:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.35,0:10:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The one who decides...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.77,0:10:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,should be the president.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.04,0:10:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.23,0:10:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Miorine...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.59,0:10:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Who cares if we sell weapons?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.84,0:10:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't like it, you're free to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.05,0:10:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No way! We're all in this together!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.84,0:10:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? It's my company, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.11,0:10:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,If that's how it is,\Nyou're the one who should leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.57,0:10:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.42,0:10:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.62,0:10:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Miorine!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.04,0:10:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Martin!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.84,0:10:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.92,0:10:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll leave the details of the\Nregistration papers to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.71,0:10:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Lilique, you'll open the company's\Nbank account.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.64,0:11:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And help Martin with the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.84,0:11:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.40,0:11:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.51,0:11:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Is anyone here a decent artist?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.81,0:11:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Design us a company logo. Make it stylish.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.55,0:11:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Suletta... and the rest...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.14,0:11:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't lump us together!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.22,0:11:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Make a PR video that will\Nrid Gundams of their bad image.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.39,0:11:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got two weeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.64,0:11:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Two weeks?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.06,0:11:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Nail down everything before\Nmy lousy father changes his mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.23,0:11:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't slack off!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.25,0:11:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,That bossy little Spacian turd!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.55,0:11:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.70,0:11:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought this was a garbage dump.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.06,0:11:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.67,0:11:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not making this fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.25,0:11:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Picking up litter?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.44,0:11:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,How noble.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.44,0:11:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll pick up where you left off.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.40,0:11:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.65,0:11:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for the trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.53,0:12:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to our House.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.12,0:12:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You can shower there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.79,0:12:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't lick the boots of a wimp\Nwho was afraid to duel me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.12,0:12:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I only avoided it because\NI thought I could leave it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.08,0:12:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.54,0:12:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Call me if you change your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.34,0:12:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I happen to be...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.28,0:12:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,quite fond of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.51,0:12:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't need anyone's pity!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.77,0:12:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.81,0:12:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I sent you some Beguir-Pentes\Nand a Michaelis.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.02,0:12:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They're bringing anti-Gundam weapons too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.49,0:12:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I've no intention of seizing it in a duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.68,0:12:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Do it whatever way you like.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.14,0:12:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But don't forget.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.02,0:12:47.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The Gundams must be erased\Nfrom this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.87,0:12:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.46,0:12:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,He's far too narrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.59,0:12:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,In his vision...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.55,0:12:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,and his ideas.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.01,0:13:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And our Cathedra shall deny all Gundams.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.81,0:13:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Gundam...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.51,0:13:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,A mobile suit that kills its pilot.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.31,0:13:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The GUND Format...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.82,0:13:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to know more.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.74,0:13:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,As soon as your company is ready,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.48,0:13:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Peil's development team and the Pharact
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.85,0:13:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,will be officially transferred to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.75,0:13:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I look forward to working with you,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.58,0:13:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Belmeria Winston.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.71,0:13:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.86,0:13:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What brings you here today?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.67,0:13:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to learn more about Gundams.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.76,0:13:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Mobile suits called Gundams that\Ncripple their pilots' minds and bodies...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.93,0:13:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,the Vanadis Institute that created them...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.85,0:13:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,and the people we call witches\Nare all to be abhorred.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.43,0:13:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what the public believes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.31,0:13:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,If they were defective,\Nthey could have been improved.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.76,0:14:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,So why did they reject that...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.72,0:14:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,and try to eliminate them\Nby concocting that agreement?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.12,0:14:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,And why did the witches
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.93,0:14:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,create the Gundams in the first place?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.73,0:14:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.37,0:14:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't call them "witches."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.73,0:14:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Does that mean you're a witch too?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.58,0:14:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I was merely...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.79,0:14:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,enthralled by the GUND's ideals...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.11,0:14:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,and have simply\Nbeen imitating what they did.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.26,0:14:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The GUND's ideals...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.14,0:14:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you tell me more about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.19,0:14:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,So you can't help hanging\Naround this place after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.57,0:14:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you know about\Nthe ideals behind GUND technology?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.96,0:14:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,My father told me most of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.03,0:14:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,He trusts you, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.64,0:14:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I worked hard to earn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.33,0:14:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And? Who are you groveling to today?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.48,0:14:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I came to grovel to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.84,0:15:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,There are customers who want Gundams.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.92,0:15:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,If you can develop a machine\Nequal in strength to the Aerial
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.20,0:15:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,that outperformed\NJeturk's and Peil's mobile suits,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.60,0:15:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,many buyers would want to obtain it\Neven without Cathedra's approval.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.14,0:15:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm sure you're aware of\Nour monetary situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.69,0:15:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't we work together?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.36,0:15:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Not only can I give you financial\Nsupport until you're on your feet,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.85,0:15:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I can lend you any personnel you need.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.78,0:15:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't sound too bad, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.64,0:15:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,And what's in it for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.43,0:15:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Gundams are a game changer that will\Nrevitalize the stagnant weapons industry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.00,0:15:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The group will never grow\Nfurther if it misses this chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.27,0:15:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't your Daddy allergic to Gundams?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.41,0:15:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll bring him around.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.61,0:15:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I regard it as my filial duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.59,0:15:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Back in the day,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.43,0:15:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,we submitted a project plan together\Nin a business competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.61,0:15:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,A secret from everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.13,0:15:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't remember a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.56,0:15:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The plan was accepted,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.68,0:15:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,but our fathers found out and scolded us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.52,0:16:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, I haven't forgotten that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.36,0:16:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,If you and I work together,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.05,0:16:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe we can bring about\Na better future than our fathers.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.48,0:16:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Miorine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.24,0:16:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,There. You can clearly see\Nwhere it's been edited.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.66,0:16:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Martin, there are mistakes here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.82,0:16:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw, man...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.91,0:16:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.16,0:16:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and bury the hatchet!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.78,0:16:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And where's the Princess, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.28,0:16:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The two weeks are up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.75,0:16:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll bet she got fed up\Nand ran away to Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.76,0:16:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Ms. Miorine wouldn't...\NShe wouldn't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.83,0:16:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You haven't known her\Nlong enough to say for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.35,0:16:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Looking for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.98,0:16:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Miorine!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.18,0:16:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I believed in you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.65,0:16:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Miorine--
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.40,0:16:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You're annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.89,0:16:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.94,0:16:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you decided?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.19,0:16:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,How we're going to sell the Gundams.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.99,0:16:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,There are two ways to earn revenue.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.00,0:17:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,The first is to sell Gundams as weapons.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.42,0:17:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, we'll ask no\Nquestions about who we sell to.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.80,0:17:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,And the other option...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.43,0:17:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\an8}Good afternoon, Spacians.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.50,0:17:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\an8}We are the staff of Vanadis,\Nan institute for Permet research.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.22,0:17:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\an8}Almost a century has passed{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.22,0:17:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell is this video?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.76,0:17:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1\an8}since we expanded our biosphere into space{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.76,0:17:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.98,0:17:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,And we humans...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.98,0:17:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}The one who created the Gundams.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.89,0:17:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}...have always struggled to\Nsurvive the harsh space environment.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.70,0:17:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Weightlessness, vacuum,\Natmospheric composition,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.90,0:17:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}space radiation...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.23,0:17:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even with expensive\Nvaccines and implant apps, {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.52,0:17:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}we can barely suppress\Nthe disorders themselves.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.38,0:17:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Which is why the GUND medical technology{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.62,0:17:52.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}that we're proposing\Ncould be a technology of hope{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.99,0:17:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}for supplementing the fragility\Nof the human body.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.22,0:17:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,GUND medical technology?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.88,0:18:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}GUND technology has the potential\Nnot only to expand the biosphere,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.54,0:18:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but also to reconcile\Nthe divisions and disparities{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.96,0:18:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}between the people of Earth and space.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.60,0:18:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We hope you will join us in\Ngrasping hold of this ray of light{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.61,0:18:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}that could lead to a better\Nfuture for all humanity.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.29,0:18:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the other way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.58,0:18:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Pursuing the true ideals behind the Gundam...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.59,0:18:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll complete the GUND medical\Ntechnology and send it out into the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.63,0:18:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,But that means...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.18,0:18:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Using Gundams to save lives?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.05,0:18:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,A mobile suit...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.43,0:18:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,that saves lives...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.22,0:18:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know if the world\Nwill accept it or not. However...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.30,0:18:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,it's worth a try.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.23,0:18:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,First of all, it's great to take\Na different path from my lousy father.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.03,0:18:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take on all responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.28,0:18:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Any objections?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.83,0:19:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}GUND-ARM... GUND-ARM...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.74,0:19:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A ray of hope{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.86,0:19:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}GUND-ARM... GUND-ARM...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.66,0:19:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Forward to the future{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.18,0:19:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's safe... to pilot!\NIt's reliable... to use!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.18,0:19:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It can fly! It can dance! Aerial!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.94,0:19:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}GUND-ARM, Inc.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.90,0:19:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}is dedicated to the medical use\Nof GUND technology.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.41,0:19:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,We've finished drafting the business plan\Nfor investors and streaming the PR video.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.66,0:19:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The articles of incorporation\Nand various applications are done.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.63,0:19:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Once the school accepts\Nour application for a student startup,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.24,0:19:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,the company will be officially established.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.29,0:19:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you all for your hard work!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.71,0:19:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.62,0:20:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,All we did was help with the video, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.39,0:20:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,A medical company\Nthat handles GUND technology.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.13,0:20:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's better than being complicit in war.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.02,0:20:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no good or evil\Nwhen it comes to saving lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.69,0:20:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.90,0:20:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.02,0:20:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Chuchu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.82,0:20:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,In my hometown...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.16,0:20:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,there are lots of people who lost\Ntheir arms and legs in mining accidents.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.21,0:20:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,If I can make money and be useful\Nto my family, there's nothing better.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.71,0:20:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And so...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.18,0:20:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,has the food\Nfor the launch party arrived yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.80,0:20:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much, Ms. Miorine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.54,0:20:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,For what?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.83,0:20:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You worked out a plan\Nacceptable to everyone, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.71,0:20:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I just couldn't afford to lose them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.94,0:20:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,To tell the truth... this is kind of fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.65,0:21:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like joining a club,\Njust like my wish list.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.49,0:21:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot. This isn't for amusement.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.83,0:21:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.12,0:21:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.59,0:21:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Miorine?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.15,0:21:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.47,0:21:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,As directed, I've added new regulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.68,0:21:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Article 53, paragraph 3 of the Student\NBusiness Startup Regulations...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.38,0:21:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,"Safety verification of new technology\Nused in student businesses."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.69,0:21:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Miorine can't start her company now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.86,0:21:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The Gundam will revert\Nto being group property.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.61,0:21:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Now Mr. Sarius just has to dispose of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.99,0:21:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel kind of sorry for Miss Miorine.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.83,0:21:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.64,0:21:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,We can all help cheer her up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.23,0:21:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let him dispose of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.50,0:21:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The Gundam will eventually be needed\Nby myself and the group.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.17,0:22:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be taking over Miorine's company.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.13,0:22:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And if she refuses?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.50,0:22:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,There's only one solution, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.13,0:22:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Though I doubt that's what Shaddiq wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.76,0:22:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,But we're prepared for what comes next.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.14,0:22:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll simply seize the Gundam...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.73,0:22:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,from Miorine's hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.88,0:23:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Next time on {\i0}\NMobile Suit Gundam: The Witch from Mercury,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.47,0:24:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"If I Could Take One Step Toward You."{\i0}
